comments: Looney (GSW) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and marginal upper body contact occurs as the pick is set.

Replay review of the foul called on McDaniels (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. McDaniels removes his hand from Thompson's (GSW) hip and marginal arm contact occurs after the release of Thompson's shot attempt.  Neither team had imminent possession and play resumes with a jump ball.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on McDaniels (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. McDaniels (MIN) avoids making body contact with Thompson (GSW) as he legally contests the jump shot attempt. The game resumes with a jump ball.
Looney (GSW) jumps into McDaniels (MIN) and initiates body contact that affects his ability to pursue the jump ball.
Looney (GSW) is moving alongside Conley's (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs  as they come together during the drive.
Looney (GSW) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Reid (MIN) after the release.
Lamb (GSW) brings his hands toward McDaniels (MIN) and marginal body contact occurs as he releases away to roll.
Looney (GSW) is moving alongside Reid's (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
McDaniels (MIN) and Poole (GSW) mutually engage off-ball  during the inbound and marginal body contact occurs.
Conley (MIN) makes marginal contact with DiVincenzo (GSW) while attempting to apply defensive pressure.
Conley (MIN) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Thompson (GSW) engages with Edwards (MIN) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as he releases away.
Edwards (MIN) places his arm around Thompson's (GSW) waist and marginal contact occurs as they engage off-ball during the inbound.
Thompson (GSW) contests McLaughlin's (MIN) jump shot and marginal contact occurs after the release and follow-through.
McLaughlin (MIN) wraps his arm around DiVincenzo's (GSW) body as he attempts to get to the pass and delivers contact that affects his FOM.
Edwards (MIN) swipes down and wrist contact occurs with Thompson (GSW) as they come together.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Poole (GSW).
